  "detailed_description": "Motorcycles, guns, monsters and bikini-babes. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nLed It Rain is first person shooter motorcycle driving racing game. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFaster you drive and shoot monsters more score you obtain. Monsters include zombies, devils, skeletons, werewolves, chainsaw-maniacs and hilarious Wheelchair Zombiesᵀᴹ.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach race track has three laps on such levels as Depot, Crypt, Abyss, Mansion and Swamp.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLed It Rain features music by Electric Deathbeat and a theme song by Maze of Jesse Lane.",
  "about_the_game": "Motorcycles, guns, monsters and bikini-babes. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nLed It Rain is first person shooter motorcycle driving racing game. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFaster you drive and shoot monsters more score you obtain. Monsters include zombies, devils, skeletons, werewolves, chainsaw-maniacs and hilarious Wheelchair Zombiesᵀᴹ.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach race track has three laps on such levels as Depot, Crypt, Abyss, Mansion and Swamp.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLed It Rain features music by Electric Deathbeat and a theme song by Maze of Jesse Lane.",
